1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, još vas jednom sve na početku pozdravljam na našem ovom drugom susretu unutar našeg ciklusa teme o Euharistiji,Euharistija židovski korijeni i ispunjenje iščekivanja izabranog naroda.

2
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo kao što sam objasnio i ono što smo prošli puta isto nekako malo pokušali uspješno ili poluuspješno očkrinuti zajedno vrata, upravo pričati o Euharistiji i o svetoj misi

3
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] iz perspektive onoga što zapravo izabrani narod cijelo vrijeme iščekivao.

4
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Danas ćemo ići korak dalje, sjećate se prošli puta, smo pričali, pokušali smo napraviti paralelu između starog izlaska, ono prve pashe i novog izlaska, odnosno pashe koju je Krist napravio za nas u vazbenom trodnevlju

5
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ono što nam svakako ostaje i dan danas kroz vijekove, kroz Euharistiju, odnosno svetu misu.

6
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] I tamo smo govorili o novom Mojsiju, o novoj mani s neba, o novoj pashalnoj noći, o novom prinesenom kruhu ili kruh lica, božeg lica.

7
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:16,040
[SPEAKER_00] I to onako će odjekivati sada cijelo vrijeme kroz ove još neke susrete koje ćemo imati na ovu temu.

8
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] A danas imamo dosta jednu škakljivu temu.

9
00:01:19,900 --> 00:01:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto škakljivu?

10
00:01:21,739 --> 00:01:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što vrlo je važna i po meni vrlo snažna, vidite, čak se i rimuje.

11
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:51,879
[SPEAKER_00] A vrlo je škakljiva zato što ovisi koliko ću vam sjesti ova tema, možda ne samo vama, nego ako će ikada netko tko nije katolik ovo isto slušati, važno je koliko uspijem ovdje iskomunicirati temu, a to je Euharistija, odnosno posljednja večera i izgubljena izraelska plemena.

12
00:01:51,879 --> 00:02:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kako gospodin, kroz sve one znake koje si bole na posljednoj večeri, kroz svoj govor, a onda i na kraju krajeva na samoj svetoj misiji, Euharistiji, kako zapravo natrag sabire izgubljena 12 plemena Izrelovih.

13
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:22,840
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem, vrlo onako, najzgled je jedan sklizak teren, ali opet smatram vrlo važan, zato što ovdje ćemo vidjeti Euharistija ima tendenciju imati jedno univerzalno značenje.

14
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:30,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo za nas katolike, ono što ona predstavlja u sakramentalnom životu i u našem duholom životu isto tako,

15
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] nego, evo, dakle, jedan univerzalni, zaista univerzalni općeniti, općenita ponuda za svakoga tražitelja istine, ako baš tako želite.

16
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] Židova i ne židova.

17
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:52,419
[SPEAKER_00] S druge strane, zašto je ova tema isto tako važna, ne samo s obzirom na univerzalni značaj Euharistije,

18
00:02:52,419 --> 00:03:02,780
[SPEAKER_00] nego da vam, da lakše, možda vam isto sjedne, zašto Euharistija izgleda tako kako izgleda

19
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:10,879
[SPEAKER_00] i zašto je važno, zašto je važno isto tako, vjerovati da Euharistija, možemo ovako reći, dobro,

20
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] evo, sada na kraju, u kojih četrdesetak minuta, koliko će trajati ovamo izlaganje na ovu temu,

21
00:03:16,219 --> 00:03:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju možemo reći, dobro, možda znamo sada nešto eventualno više,

22
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] možda znamo i podkrijepiti neke stvari našim židovskim prijateljima,

23
00:03:25,159 --> 00:03:28,819
[SPEAKER_00] našoj židovskoj starijoj braći ili odjeljanoj braći protestantima,

24
00:03:28,819 --> 00:03:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, nekako obraniti apologetski naš odnos prema svetoj misiji, Euharistiji,

25
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:43,319
[SPEAKER_00] ali zašto onda idemo toliko daleko da govorimo i o stvarnoj kristove prisutnosti Euharistiji?

26
00:03:43,319 --> 00:03:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto se jednostavno ne možemo zaustaviti kao na nekom spomenu,

27
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:54,120
[SPEAKER_00] na nekom Isusovom projektu u kojem On skuplja 12 izgubljenih Izraelovih plemena?

28
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:59,020
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto idemo još više i govorimo o konkretnoj kristove prisutnosti

29
00:03:59,020 --> 00:04:00,699
[SPEAKER_00] pod prilikama kruha i vina.

30
00:04:00,699 --> 00:04:05,699
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ovo sada na početku neka ostane onako nekako u vašim glavama,

31
00:04:05,699 --> 00:04:09,020
[SPEAKER_00] kako bismo mogli lijepo na kraju sve zaključiti.

32
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje se navješta Euharistija?

33
00:04:14,699 --> 00:04:18,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ne govorim o našem katoličkom pristupu,

34
00:04:18,699 --> 00:04:20,819
[SPEAKER_00] koji imate na bitno netu, by the way.

35
00:04:20,819 --> 00:04:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne govorim o našem katoličkom pristupu

36
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,879
[SPEAKER_00] i katoličkim očima gledano na neke stvari svaki put

37
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:28,060
[SPEAKER_00] kad neko u starom zavitu netko nešto jede,

38
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,560
[SPEAKER_00] to je za nas Euharistija.

39
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, legitimno. Sve ok.

40
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali židovu i protestantu to ništa ne znači.

41
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] Što njemu znači Adam i Eva u Edenu?

42
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi puta konzumacija neke hrane

43
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:43,459
[SPEAKER_00] i već tu vidimo neki predznak Euharistije.

44
00:04:43,459 --> 00:04:45,680
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo reći, da, drvo, stablo,

45
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] kao u Edenu ovdje je stablo križa,

46
00:04:48,019 --> 00:04:50,439
[SPEAKER_00] zabranje novoće ne smije se jesti,

47
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,680
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje je sada dopušteno,

48
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,540
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, Isusovu tijelo i krv,

49
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] taj ploc križa i tako dalje,

50
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] ili ilija koji je umoran,

51
00:04:57,019 --> 00:04:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa mu donosi onaj gavran ili vran,

52
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,459
[SPEAKER_00] ili koja je već, ne znam, ptica bila,

53
00:05:00,459 --> 00:05:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] moram pitan biblijske ornitologe,

54
00:05:02,699 --> 00:05:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] točno,

55
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:07,220
[SPEAKER_00] donese mu kruh isto, slika Euharistije.

56
00:05:07,220 --> 00:05:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki put kad neko nešto jede,

57
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] nama je to Euharistija.

58
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ok.

59
00:05:11,060 --> 00:05:12,759
[SPEAKER_00] legitimno za katolike.

60
00:05:12,759 --> 00:05:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ne možete tako s time

61
00:05:15,980 --> 00:05:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] ići servirano nekom židovu i nekom protestantu.

62
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,060
[SPEAKER_00] On u tom ne vidio Euharistiju.

63
00:05:21,060 --> 00:05:21,879
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto bi uvidio?

64
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:23,819
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je ovdje vrlo važno,

65
00:05:23,819 --> 00:05:27,439
[SPEAKER_00] i nastojao sam biti vrlo sofisticiran i oprezan

66
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] na ovoj temi,

67
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] da opet ne ispadne,

68
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] da nešto tjeramo,

69
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:32,759
[SPEAKER_00] kada tjeramo vodu na svoj mlin.

70
00:05:33,139 --> 00:05:34,439
[SPEAKER_00] Kada ovo sad tumačimo,

71
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:36,120
[SPEAKER_00] jel Euharistija kao povratak

72
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,399
[SPEAKER_00] 12 izgubjenih Izraevih plemena,

73
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] kao nešto opet ide nekako u naš kut,

74
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:41,399
[SPEAKER_00] jel,

75
00:05:41,399 --> 00:05:43,180
[SPEAKER_00] katolički kut.

76
00:05:43,180 --> 00:05:44,720
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, tako da, evo,

77
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,680
[SPEAKER_00] čisto da znate,

78
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,740
[SPEAKER_00] bio sam dosta oprezan ovdje.

79
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:49,040
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo vidjeti prije svega,

80
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] i zašto je, kažem,

81
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,639
[SPEAKER_00] istova tema važna,

82
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:55,439
[SPEAKER_00] da je Euharistija,

83
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:57,060
[SPEAKER_00] da pokažemo da Euharistija

84
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] nije samo opet neki katolički produkt,

85
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,220
[SPEAKER_00] nešto što je sa nama

86
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] nekako puhnulo u glavu,

87
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,319
[SPEAKER_00] pa smo stavili,

88
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] ili smo nekako pre rekli,

89
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] ili pre krivo protumačili

90
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,379
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je Isus govorio

91
00:06:08,379 --> 00:06:09,620
[SPEAKER_00] i činio na posljednjoj večeri,

92
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,399
[SPEAKER_00] je to nešto što zaista

93
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:13,860
[SPEAKER_00] znakovi toga konkretno postoje

94
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:14,779
[SPEAKER_00] u prorocima.

95
00:06:14,779 --> 00:06:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] Bez ikakvih simbolike,

96
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:19,459
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo onako nedvojbeno,

97
00:06:19,459 --> 00:06:20,439
[SPEAKER_00] nedvosmisleno,

98
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] proroci govore

99
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:25,060
[SPEAKER_00] kako će preko konkretne gozbe

100
00:06:25,060 --> 00:06:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] svi narodi biti spašeni.

101
00:06:27,279 --> 00:06:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] I to na koji način.

102
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:30,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ta gozba nije bilo kakva,

103
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] ima određenu simboliku,

104
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] određene znakove,

105
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] određene geste.

106
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] Prije svega,

107
00:06:35,519 --> 00:06:37,439
[SPEAKER_00] koji je problem

108
00:06:37,439 --> 00:06:39,819
[SPEAKER_00] izgubljenih plemena Izraelovih?

109
00:06:39,819 --> 00:06:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] Evo čisto ja kratki,

110
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] kratki povijesni presjek

111
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:45,040
[SPEAKER_00] da vam isto sjedne,

112
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] zašto su plemena izgubljena

113
00:06:47,420 --> 00:06:51,040
[SPEAKER_00] i gdje se ona nalaze tada u Isusovo vrijeme,

114
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] a gdje se nalaze danas.

115
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:58,720
[SPEAKER_00] Od 1000 do 922. prije Krista

116
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:01,600
[SPEAKER_00] imamo ono snažno Davidovo kraljevstvo.

117
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] Davidovu dinastiju

118
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] iz svih 12 izraovih plemena

119
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,720
[SPEAKER_00] u tom periodu,

120
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:09,680
[SPEAKER_00] od 1000 do 922. prije Krista,

121
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,759
[SPEAKER_00] svih 12 plemena je pod Davidom

122
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:14,060
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovim sinom Salomonom.

123
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:16,779
[SPEAKER_00] 922. prije Krista

124
00:07:16,779 --> 00:07:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi prvi puta

125
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] do podjele kraljevstva.

126
00:07:21,699 --> 00:07:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

127
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,620
[SPEAKER_00] 10 plemena Izraelovih

128
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] ide u takozvano sjeverno kraljevstvo,

129
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] koje se zove Izrael,

130
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:31,639
[SPEAKER_00] a dva preostala plemena Izraelova

131
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] idu u južno kraljevstvo,

132
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,439
[SPEAKER_00] koje se zove Juda.

133
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,060
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

134
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:38,100
[SPEAKER_00] 10 plemena je u Izraelu, sjever,

135
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] i jug, Juda,

136
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] dva preostala plemena.

137
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] Oko 750. prije Krista,

138
00:07:44,980 --> 00:07:46,740
[SPEAKER_00] kada malo gledate Stari Zavjet,

139
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:49,459
[SPEAKER_00] proroci su već počeli

140
00:07:49,459 --> 00:07:50,379
[SPEAKER_00] nagovještati

141
00:07:50,379 --> 00:07:53,160
[SPEAKER_00] da će gospodi dopustiti

142
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:55,540
[SPEAKER_00] da Izrael i Juda,

143
00:07:55,540 --> 00:07:57,439
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, svih zajedno

144
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:58,939
[SPEAKER_00] 12 plemena Izraelovih,

145
00:07:58,939 --> 00:08:01,560
[SPEAKER_00] će biti progonjeno,

146
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,660
[SPEAKER_00] bit će, dakle,

147
00:08:02,660 --> 00:08:05,060
[SPEAKER_00] odvedeno u sužanjstvo,

148
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:07,540
[SPEAKER_00] ali da će opet biti

149
00:08:07,540 --> 00:08:08,740
[SPEAKER_00] skupljeni zajedno,

150
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] da će se opet zajedno

151
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] natrag sabrati.

152
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] I 722. događa se

153
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:16,399
[SPEAKER_00] Asirsko sužanjstvo.

154
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:17,220
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

155
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:18,660
[SPEAKER_00] Asirski osvajač,

156
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] što radi,

157
00:08:19,199 --> 00:08:21,939
[SPEAKER_00] 10 Izraelovih plemena

158
00:08:21,939 --> 00:08:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] su, dakle,

159
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,160
[SPEAKER_00] odvedeni u Asiriju

160
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,360
[SPEAKER_00] i što?

161
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,839
[SPEAKER_00] Razbacani su

162
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:27,759
[SPEAKER_00] među pogane,

163
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:28,339
[SPEAKER_00] kaže se,

164
00:08:28,339 --> 00:08:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

165
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] razbacani su među pogane,

166
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] izgubljeni su među

167
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,679
[SPEAKER_00] među poganima.

168
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

169
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,840
[SPEAKER_00] sjever,

170
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] 10 plemena,

171
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,200
[SPEAKER_00] najviše zapravo

172
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,259
[SPEAKER_00] od 12 plemena

173
00:08:39,259 --> 00:08:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] Izraelovih,

174
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] a 587. prije Krista

175
00:08:42,139 --> 00:08:43,080
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi do

176
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] Babilonskog sužanjstva

177
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] i preostala

178
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] dva plemena

179
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] koja se nalaze

180
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:48,120
[SPEAKER_00] na jugu,

181
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:48,580
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

182
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] Juda,

183
00:08:51,019 --> 00:08:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] su odvedeni

184
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,480
