[SPEAKER_00] Neki se već i smatraju poganima,

1067
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne više židovima.

1068
00:27:39,019 --> 00:27:40,980
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je važno to,

1069
00:27:40,980 --> 00:27:42,640
[SPEAKER_00] neko od vas možda pod NK

1070
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] jeste isto židova da ne zna.

1071
00:27:44,019 --> 00:27:45,299
