[SPEAKER_00] Moramo to provjeriti.

1074
00:27:47,900 --> 00:27:49,759
[SPEAKER_00] E sada,

1075
00:27:49,759 --> 00:27:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] što mislite,

1076
