1082
00:28:01,279 --> 00:28:02,339
[SPEAKER_00] o mesijanskoj gozbi.

1083
00:28:02,339 --> 00:28:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo što sam malo prije pročitao.

1084
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] Što mislite,

1085
00:28:05,420 --> 00:28:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] koje čuda,

1086
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:06,700
[SPEAKER_00] koje znamenje?

1087
00:28:06,700 --> 00:28:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno od najvažnijih,

1088
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] najsnažnijih čuda koje čini.

1089
00:28:10,059 --> 00:28:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nije baš bilo kapo.

1090
00:28:12,299 --> 00:28:12,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1091
00:28:12,819 --> 00:28:15,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kad Isus dva put hrani mnoštvo.

1092
00:28:15,279 --> 00:28:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo jednostavno.

1093
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dva put hrani mnoštvo.

1094
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Slažite da dva put hrani mnoštvo?

1095
00:28:19,539 --> 00:28:20,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo jedan put,

1096
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego dva put.

1097
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte sad ovo.

1098
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, prvi puta,

1099
00:28:24,619 --> 00:28:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] ako se sjećate,

1100
00:28:25,519 --> 00:28:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] prvi puta hrani mnoštvo,

1101
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] Matej 14 i Marko 6

1102
00:28:30,019 --> 00:28:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] o tome govore,

1103
00:28:30,700 --> 00:28:31,759
[SPEAKER_00] kad imamo pet kruhova

1104
00:28:31,759 --> 00:28:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] i dvije ribice,

1105
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] a drugi puta hrani mnoštvo,

1106
00:28:34,380 --> 00:28:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] Matej 15 i Marko 8,

1107
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:37,839
[SPEAKER_00] kad ima sedam kruhova

1108
00:28:37,839 --> 00:28:38,799
[SPEAKER_00] i nekoliko ribica.

1109
00:28:38,799 --> 00:28:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] E sada imamo malo u simboliku.

1110
00:28:40,579 --> 00:28:41,759
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo se malo poigrati

1111
00:28:41,759 --> 00:28:42,680
