[SPEAKER_00] što to zapravo konkretno znači

1113
00:28:44,519 --> 00:28:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] i koja je povezanost

1114
00:28:45,500 --> 00:28:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] s ome što je Izaija rekao.

1115
00:28:46,980 --> 00:28:48,720
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju kraja Isus se to pita.

1116
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] Isus, kada očini ta čuda,

1117
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] pita svoje učenike,

1118
00:28:52,599 --> 00:28:54,160
[SPEAKER_00] jeste skužili što sam sad napravio?

1119
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Marko 8, 14 do 22.

1120
00:28:58,019 --> 00:29:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] A apostoli zaboraviše podjeti kruha.

1121
00:29:00,559 --> 00:29:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] Oni uvijek nemaju kruha,

1122
00:29:02,859 --> 00:29:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] traže žice druge da jedu,

1123
00:29:04,759 --> 00:29:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] nikak da ulove ribe,

1124
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] pravi katolici.

1125
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:08,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1126
00:29:08,759 --> 00:29:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nostop gladi tamo tržu nešto i tako.

1127
00:29:11,599 --> 00:29:12,759
[SPEAKER_00] Onda Isu ima s njima problema,

1128
00:29:12,759 --> 00:29:14,680
[SPEAKER_00] onda ih nostop pred farizejeva

1129
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] mora opravdavati

1130
00:29:15,559 --> 00:29:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] i vuču neke aseve iz rukava.

1131
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:19,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, dobro.

1132
00:29:19,240 --> 00:29:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] E sad.

1133
00:29:20,559 --> 00:29:22,299
[SPEAKER_00] A zaboraviše podjeti kruha.

1134
00:29:22,299 --> 00:29:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] Imali su samo jedan kruh

1135
