1136
00:29:24,759 --> 00:29:26,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dato ih Isus opomenu.

1137
00:29:26,819 --> 00:29:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, čujete se kvasa farizejskog

1138
00:29:29,079 --> 00:29:30,180
[SPEAKER_00] i kvasa Herodova.

1139
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] Oni zamišljali među sobom govorahu.

1140
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kruha nemamo.

1141
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, pusti sad to o farizejima,

1142
00:29:34,859 --> 00:29:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] gladni smo.

1143
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:37,240
[SPEAKER_00] Mislite, ponekad mi malo smiješilo.

1144
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:38,200
[SPEAKER_00] Dijelo je, ali dobro.

1145
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1146
00:29:39,859 --> 00:29:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zamijetio to Isus, pa im reče.

1147
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:44,279
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ste zamišljali što kruha nemate?

1148
00:29:44,279 --> 00:29:46,660
[SPEAKER_00] Zar još ne skvačate i ne razumijete?

1149
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] Zar vam je srce stvrnuto?

1150
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:49,700
[SPEAKER_00] Oči imate, a ne vidite.

1151
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] Uši imate, a ne čujete.

1152
00:29:50,940 --> 00:29:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] Zar se ne sjećate?

1153
00:29:52,359 --> 00:29:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam ono razlomio pet kruhova na pet tisuća,

1154
00:29:55,940 --> 00:29:58,000
