1155
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,180
[SPEAKER_00] Kažu mu dvanest.

1156
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] A kad razlovi ih sedam na četiri tisuće,

1157
00:30:02,079 --> 00:30:04,240
[SPEAKER_00] koliko punih košera ulomaka odnijeste?

1158
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,299
[SPEAKER_00] Odgovore sedam.

1159
00:30:05,299 --> 00:30:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] A učenjima još ne razumijete.

1160
00:30:07,619 --> 00:30:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jer razumijete?

1161
00:30:09,599 --> 00:30:11,339
[SPEAKER_00] Još ne razumijete?

1162
00:30:11,339 --> 00:30:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ne razumijem ja.

1163
00:30:13,799 --> 00:30:14,640
[SPEAKER_00] Zaključujemo.

1164
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo doma.

1165
00:30:15,579 --> 00:30:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1166
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:19,720
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Isus ovdje sam,

1167
