[SPEAKER_00] upravo u ovom dialogu,

1168
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] želi pokazati,

1169
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:24,859
[SPEAKER_00] napravio sam jedan znak, jedno znamenje.

1170
00:30:24,859 --> 00:30:26,640
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto sam želio poručiti time,

1171
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:27,900
[SPEAKER_00] tim hranjenjem noštva.

1172
