[SPEAKER_00] i uvijeti što konkretno.

1173
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako.

1174
00:30:30,559 --> 00:30:32,700
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo bi jednostavnije da,

1175
00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:33,740
[SPEAKER_00] ovako tablicu,

1176
00:30:33,740 --> 00:30:34,839
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam napravio tablicu,

1177
00:30:34,839 --> 00:30:35,799
[SPEAKER_00] prvo hranjenje mnoštva

1178
00:30:35,799 --> 00:30:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] i drugo hranjenje mnoštva.

1179
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] Napravimo paralelu.

1180
00:30:37,619 --> 00:30:39,240
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijemo koja je simbolika.

1181
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dobro.

1182
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, ok.

1183
00:30:43,140 --> 00:30:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, prvo hranjenje mnoštva.

1184
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo pet kruhova i dvije ribice.

1185
00:30:47,259 --> 00:30:48,759
[SPEAKER_00] U drugom hranjenju mnoštva

1186
00:30:48,759 --> 00:30:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] imamo sedam kruhova i nekoliko ribica.

1187
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] U prvom hranjenju

1188
00:30:52,380 --> 00:30:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] nahranjeno je pet tisuća ljudi.

1189
00:30:55,259 --> 00:30:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] U drugom hranjenju sa sedam kruhova

1190
00:30:57,559 --> 00:30:59,180
[SPEAKER_00] nahranjeno je četiri tisuće.

1191
00:30:59,180 --> 00:31:00,279
[SPEAKER_00] Pratite.

1192
00:31:00,279 --> 00:31:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1193
00:31:01,039 --> 00:31:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajmo dalje.

1194
00:31:02,019 --> 00:31:04,140
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo hranjenje mnoštva

1195
00:31:04,140 --> 00:31:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] se događa gdje?

1196
00:31:05,359 --> 00:31:06,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sad imamo vidjeti mjesto.

1197
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo važno, vrlo znakovito.

1198
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] Na židovskom teritoriju.

1199
00:31:09,579 --> 00:31:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i vidim to

1200
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:12,900
[SPEAKER_00] Marko 6.42 govori,

1201
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali Galilea 6.42.

1202
00:31:14,460 --> 00:31:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] I to vidimo,

1203
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] zanimljivo,

1204
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:17,400
[SPEAKER_00] i jezično se ovdje poigrava,

1205
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] da znamo da smo

1206
00:31:18,019 --> 00:31:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] na židovskom teritoriju

1207
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] kod prvog hranjenja mnoštva.

1208
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kad on za košare,

1209
