[SPEAKER_00] dakle, koliko je ostalo?

1210
00:31:23,359 --> 00:31:24,359
[SPEAKER_00] 12 košara.

1211
00:31:24,359 --> 00:31:25,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kad on za košare koristi

1212
