[SPEAKER_00] Kofinos nije grčki izraz za košare,

1216
00:31:31,980 --> 00:31:32,779
[SPEAKER_00] nego hebriski.

1217
00:31:32,779 --> 00:31:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, želi

1218
