[SPEAKER_00] 12 kofinosa je ostalo.

1219
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] I to je vrlo jednostavno.

1220
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] 12 prvo u prvom

1221
00:31:38,599 --> 00:31:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] i koga nahranio,

1222
00:31:39,759 --> 00:31:42,299
[SPEAKER_00] 12 plamena Izraela.

1223
00:31:42,299 --> 00:31:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, simbolika 12 košara,

1224
00:31:43,859 --> 00:31:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] 12 plamena Izraela.

1225
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] 12 košara je preostalo.

1226
00:31:46,599 --> 00:31:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] Imo sad na drugo.

1227
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo hranjenje mnošta,

1228
00:31:50,279 --> 00:31:51,740
[SPEAKER_00] rekao smo na hranjenoj 4.000,

1229
00:31:51,740 --> 00:31:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] i ono se događa gdje?

1230
00:31:53,460 --> 00:31:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] Na poganskom teritoriju.

1231
00:31:55,079 --> 00:31:56,180
[SPEAKER_00] Tir i Sidon.

1232
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] I košare,

1233
00:31:57,579 --> 00:31:59,200
[SPEAKER_00] Marko 8.8,

1234
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] nemaju hebriski izraz

1235
00:32:00,940 --> 00:32:02,160
[SPEAKER_00] kao u prvog hranjenju,

1236
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,259
[SPEAKER_00] nego baš konkretan

1237
00:32:03,259 --> 00:32:04,160
[SPEAKER_00] grčki izraz,

1238
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] a to je Spurida.

1239
00:32:05,319 --> 00:32:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, košare.

1240
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sedam košara.

1241
00:32:07,539 --> 00:32:09,660
[SPEAKER_00] 12 je vrlo jednostavno,

1242
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] 12 plamena Izraela ovih,

1243
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:12,019
