1244
00:32:12,019 --> 00:32:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, govori o mesijanskoj gozbi

1245
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] sa židovskim izabralim narodom.

1246
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:18,259
[SPEAKER_00] A ovdje, zašto sedam?

1247
00:32:18,259 --> 00:32:19,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje nije sad stvar simbolika

1248
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] biblijskog broja sedam savršenstva,

1249
00:32:22,079 --> 00:32:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego što?

1250
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:25,799
[SPEAKER_00] Što označilo sedam preostalih košara?

1251
00:32:25,799 --> 00:32:27,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to su poganski

1252
00:32:27,599 --> 00:32:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] da sedam je broj naroda

1253
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] koje je izabrali narod našao

1254
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] kad je ušao u kanan.

1255
00:32:33,259 --> 00:32:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] I to ono što će dijela apostolska reči 13.19.

1256
00:32:36,420 --> 00:32:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pa pošto zatre sedam naroda

1257
00:32:38,599 --> 00:32:39,660
[SPEAKER_00] u zemlji kananskoj,

1258
00:32:39,660 --> 00:32:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] ubašljeni ga u zemlji njihovoj.

1259
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] Polođeni zakonik 7.1 to i kaže.

1260
00:32:45,980 --> 00:32:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kad te gospodin Bog tvoj uvede u zemlju koju ideš da je zaposjedeš

1261
00:32:49,940 --> 00:32:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] i kad ispred tebe otjera mnoge narode

1262
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] hetite, gjergašane, amorejce, kanance, perižane, hivice

1263
00:32:57,579 --> 00:32:59,180
[SPEAKER_00] i naše najdraže jebusejce,

1264
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] sedam naroda brojnih i jačih od tebe.

1265
00:33:02,059 --> 00:33:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] Sedam naroda brojnih i jačih od tebe.

1266
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je mesijansko.

1267
00:33:05,539 --> 00:33:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je ovim dva put hrani mnoštvo

1268
00:33:08,359 --> 00:33:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] i ima, dakle, sad ovo,

1269
00:33:10,599 --> 00:33:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] a učinjima još ne razumijete.

1270
00:33:12,559 --> 00:33:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] Sad razumijete?

1271
00:33:13,380 --> 00:33:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, razumijete, dobro.

1272
00:33:15,619 --> 00:33:16,759
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je to.

1273
00:33:16,759 --> 00:33:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pretilina gozba zastiraše sve narode.

1274
00:33:20,940 --> 00:33:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] Riječ je, prvo ide židovima,

1275
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] a onda ide i poganima.

1276
00:33:25,759 --> 00:33:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] I to u toj mesijanskoj gozbi želi, dakle,

1277
00:33:29,059 --> 00:33:30,859
[SPEAKER_00] povezati jedne i druge.

1278
00:33:30,859 --> 00:33:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Zato, sada vidimo da mesijanska gozba

1279
00:33:33,599 --> 00:33:35,220
[SPEAKER_00] ima univerzalni značaj.

1280
00:33:35,220 --> 00:33:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo za židove, nego i za pogane.

1281
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:40,099
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je to sada jasno.

1282
00:33:40,099 --> 00:33:44,859
[SPEAKER_00] I zato u Matej 8.11.12 kaže ovo.

1283
00:33:44,859 --> 00:33:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] A kaže vam, mnogi će s istoka i zapada

1284
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] doći i sjesti za sol s Abrahamom,

1285
00:33:51,119 --> 00:33:53,279
[SPEAKER_00] Izakom, Jakom u kraljivstvu nebeskom.

1286
00:33:53,279 --> 00:33:55,700
[SPEAKER_00] A sinovi će kraljivstva biti izbačeni

1287
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] van u tabu.

1288
00:33:56,539 --> 00:33:59,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje će biti blač i škrgut zubi.

1289
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte sad ovo.

1290
00:34:00,539 --> 00:34:03,099
[SPEAKER_00] On govori ovdje o poganima.

1291
00:34:03,099 --> 00:34:04,440
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Jer on ne kaže,

1292
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:06,619
[SPEAKER_00] mnogi će sa sjevera i juga,

1293
00:34:06,619 --> 00:34:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] jer to su židovi, sjeverno i južno kraljivstvo,

1294
00:34:09,579 --> 00:34:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] nego s istoka i zapada,

1295
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:14,239
[SPEAKER_00] istok i zapad je riječ o poganskim narodima,

1296
00:34:14,239 --> 00:34:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] doći i sad, ovo je šokantno.

1297
00:34:16,460 --> 00:34:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Isus ovdje šokira.

1298
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,820
[SPEAKER_00] Židove, zašto?

1299
00:34:19,820 --> 00:34:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo nama najnormalnija rečenica.

1300
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što je ovo šokantno?

1301
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] Da će pogani,

1302
00:34:25,420 --> 00:34:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] nečisti, nevjernici,

1303
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] sjesti za stol

1304
00:34:29,980 --> 00:34:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] sa židovskim patrijarcima,

1305
00:34:31,699 --> 00:34:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] Abrahamom, Izakom i Jakvom.

1306
00:34:33,619 --> 00:34:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jel židovi jedu sa nežidovima?

1307
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1308
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ne.

1309
00:34:37,239 --> 00:34:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] U Isusov vrijeme, ne.

1310
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:40,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da se ne one čiste.

1311
00:34:40,059 --> 00:34:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovdje Isus šokira.

1312
00:34:41,639 --> 00:34:42,679
[SPEAKER_00] Kako će pogani?

1313
00:34:42,679 --> 00:34:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to ne sa bilo kojim židovima.

1314
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,320
[SPEAKER_00] Nego sa pravocima naše vjere.

1315
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

1316
00:34:47,119 --> 00:34:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i zato je ovdje riječ

1317
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:51,760
[SPEAKER_00] kraljivstvo, nebesko-mesijanska,

1318
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,059
[SPEAKER_00] nadnaravna gozba.

1319
00:34:53,059 --> 00:34:54,820
[SPEAKER_00] Nadnaravna gozba.

1320
00:34:54,820 --> 00:34:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] Po čemu znamo da mesijanska gozba

1321
00:34:57,039 --> 00:34:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] nije ovozemaljska gozba,

1322
00:34:58,519 --> 00:35:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što sam pročitao kod proroka Izaije,

1323
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] nego nadnaravna,

1324
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ta gozba,

1325
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

1326
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] će maknuti zastručno,

1327
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] zastiraše sve narode,

1328
00:35:06,599 --> 00:35:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] to ne može obično naklopiti u McDonald'su.

1329
00:35:08,539 --> 00:35:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1330
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] uništiće smrt za svakda tom gozbom.

1331
00:35:12,139 --> 00:35:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

1332
00:35:12,579 --> 00:35:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, recite mi koji obrok

1333
00:35:14,639 --> 00:35:16,099
[SPEAKER_00] zemaljski to može učiniti.

1334
00:35:16,099 --> 00:35:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i kod proroka Izaije,

1335
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:20,800
[SPEAKER_00] mesijanska gozba jednako nadnaravna gozba.

1336
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:23,119
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, čisto da znate.

1337
00:35:23,119 --> 00:35:23,360
[SPEAKER_00] Evo.

1338
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, i sada pogledajte,

1339
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:28,159
[SPEAKER_00] nebeska gozba u židovskoj tradiciji.

1340
00:35:28,159 --> 00:35:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] Opet ću malo konzultirati

1341
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] židovske spise i židovske predaje.

1342
00:35:32,099 --> 00:35:33,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo Bibliju.

1343
00:35:33,519 --> 00:35:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1344
00:35:34,719 --> 00:35:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] spise zove

1345
00:35:36,099 --> 00:35:38,699
[SPEAKER_00] Egzodus Rabah 25.8.

1346
00:35:38,699 --> 00:35:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže ovo.

1347
00:35:39,559 --> 00:35:42,099
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo objašnjenje,

1348
00:35:42,099 --> 00:35:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo lako, lijepo.

1349
00:35:43,179 --> 00:35:44,900
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo objašnjenje riječi,

1350
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] on će prebivati u visinama.

1351
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kontekst,

1352
00:35:48,300 --> 00:35:50,860
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje se želi objasniti

1353
00:35:50,860 --> 00:35:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] iz proroka Izaije 33.16.

1354
00:35:52,679 --> 00:35:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] Rečenica,

1355
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] on će prebivati u visinama.

1356
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjet ćemo, dakle,

1357
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je ovdje židovi,

1358
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] neovisno sad samo i o svetome pismu,

1359
00:36:00,820 --> 00:36:01,940
[SPEAKER_00] nego i u svojoj tradiciji,

1360
00:36:01,940 --> 00:36:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] su svjesni toga

1361
00:36:03,460 --> 00:36:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] da nije riječ

1362
00:36:04,579 --> 00:36:06,139
[SPEAKER_00] o političkoj gozbi,

1363
00:36:06,139 --> 00:36:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] diplomatskoj,

1364
00:36:07,159 --> 00:36:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] o političkom mesiji

1365
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] i da je ta gozba nadnaravna,

1366
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti u visinama,

1367
00:36:12,099 --> 00:36:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] u kraljevstvu nebeskom.

1368
00:36:13,519 --> 00:36:14,320
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1369
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] drugo objašnjenje riječi,

1370
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:16,639
[SPEAKER_00] on će prebivati u visinama.

1371
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pisano je,

1372
00:36:17,559 --> 00:36:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] da gospodin bog tvoj vodite u dobru zemlju,

1373
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] ponovljanje zakonik 8.7,

1374
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] da vidiš stol koji je pripremljen na nebu,

1375
00:36:25,599 --> 00:36:26,739
[SPEAKER_00] kao što se kaže,

1376
00:36:26,739 --> 00:36:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] ići ću pred gospodinom u zemlji živih,

1377
00:36:30,219 --> 00:36:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] pardon,

1378
00:36:30,519 --> 00:36:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] psalam 116.

1379
00:36:31,699 --> 00:36:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] On,

1380
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:33,320
[SPEAKER_00] bog,

1381
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] kao da će sjediti nad patrijarcima,

1382
00:36:36,019 --> 00:36:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] a patrijarci i svi pravednici će sjediti u njemu samome.

1383
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo mistično.

1384
00:36:41,900 --> 00:36:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što se kaže,

1385
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] pred tvojim su ležali nogama,

1386
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] ponovljanje zakonik 33.3,

1387
00:36:46,199 --> 00:36:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] i on će im davati hrane.

1388
00:36:48,539 --> 00:36:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin u kraljevstvu nebeskom u visinama će hraniti pravednike.

1389
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:56,860
[SPEAKER_00] Donje će, što?

1390
00:36:56,860 --> 00:37:00,280
[SPEAKER_00] Donje će im plod iz Edenskog vrta.

1391
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:03,280
[SPEAKER_00] Evo sad, ovdje vi katolici imate dopuštenje

1392
00:37:03,280 --> 00:37:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] smatrati ono što se već kod Adama i Eve dogodilo,

1393
00:37:06,019 --> 00:37:07,300
[SPEAKER_00] da je predznak Euharistije.

1394
00:37:07,300 --> 00:37:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] Sami židovi svoje tradicije lijepo ovdje kažu.

1395
00:37:10,940 --> 00:37:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Donje će im plod iz Edenskog vrta

1396
00:37:13,199 --> 00:37:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] i hraniće ih iz drva života.

1397
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] Tko će biti...

1398
00:37:17,300 --> 00:37:18,219
[SPEAKER_00] Evo je sad zadimljivo.

1399
00:37:18,219 --> 00:37:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je ovako simpatišno malo.

1400
00:37:19,659 --> 00:37:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] I sada pitanje je,

1401
00:37:21,079 --> 00:37:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] tko će biti prvi koji će...

1402
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo reći, koji će se pomoliti na početku ručka, gozbe, jel?

1403
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, tko će biti prvi koji će dati blagoslov i zahvalu?

1404
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako.

1405
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] Svi će ponizno zamoliti Boga da odredi onoga koji će izreći blagoslov i zahvaliti.

1406
00:37:37,639 --> 00:37:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] E sada ide ovako.

1407
00:37:39,579 --> 00:37:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] On će odrediti Mihajla, Arkadžela Mihajla.

1408
00:37:42,019 --> 00:37:46,320
[SPEAKER_00] Onda će Mihajl, kaže, ne, odrediti Gabriela.

1409
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] Gabriela će odrediti patriarhija.

1410
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] A oni, patriarci, će dati čast Davidu.

1411
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:54,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, opet mesijanski lik.

1412
00:37:54,880 --> 00:38:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] Govoreći, dosto da i priliči se da zemaljski kralj blagoslovi i pozdravi nebeskog kralja.

1413
00:38:01,579 --> 00:38:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] Oni će predati čašu Davidu, koji će reći, uzet ću čašu spasenja i zazvati ime gospodine.

1414
00:38:09,719 --> 00:38:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo snažno ovaj dio iz židovske tradicije.

1415
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mesijanska gozba kao nadnaravna gozba.

1416
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, ko će se tamo sjediti i kako će se ovdje prepirati, ko će se pomoliti na početku.

1417
00:38:19,619 --> 00:38:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kao i mi, ono, kad smo kod nekog.

1418
00:38:21,539 --> 00:38:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ko će se pomoliti, ne ti, ne ti svečanik, pa se pomoliti.

1419
00:38:24,059 --> 00:38:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1420
00:38:25,039 --> 00:38:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, e sada, konkretno, pred sam kraj finale, a to je ovo.

1421
00:38:31,699 --> 00:38:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] Posljednja večera, ja vam ovo sa mesijanskom gozbom jasno, je li tako?

1422
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, koja je važna, dakle, preko mesijanske gozbe, to je ključ.

1423
00:38:40,639 --> 00:38:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] To je oruđe, alat, metoda, kojom gospodin, vidimo preko proroka i u samoživskoj tradiciji je to opisano,

1424
00:38:48,519 --> 00:38:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] će sabrati raspršena Izrailova plemena.

1425
00:38:52,059 --> 00:38:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jelimo sad vidjeti po čemu posljednja večera, dakle, ima prizvuk i jest mesijanska gozba,

1426
00:38:58,300 --> 00:39:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] i svaka je uharistija, i, dakle, polovno skupljanje plemena.

1427
00:39:02,079 --> 00:39:02,780
[SPEAKER_00] Na koji način?

1428
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] Marko 14, 17 od 25.

1429
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:12,340
[SPEAKER_00] A uvečer dođe on s 12-toricom, naravno, ne s trojicom, s šestoricom, 12-toricom.

1430
00:39:12,340 --> 00:39:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da bude sve po PS-u.

1431
00:39:13,619 --> 00:39:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] Molim?

1432
00:39:14,420 --> 00:39:16,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ima neko-neko kakvo pitanje.

1433
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da, recite.

1434
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je?

1435
00:39:21,539 --> 00:39:22,179
[SPEAKER_00] Petorku.

1436
00:39:22,179 --> 00:39:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1437
00:39:24,699 --> 00:39:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1438
00:39:25,880 --> 00:39:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i dok pijahu za stolom, te blagovahu, reče Isus.

1439
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] Zaista kažem vam, jedan će me od vas izdati.

1440
00:39:33,659 --> 00:39:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] Koji stavlom blaguje?

1441
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1442
00:39:38,860 --> 00:39:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] O žalost će ni stavlom govoriti ja za drugim.

1443
00:39:41,619 --> 00:39:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da nisam ja.

1444
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] A od im reče, jedan od dvane storice koji umače sa mnom u zdjelicu.

1445
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] Sin čovječi istina odlazi kako je o njemu pisano, ali ja o čovjeku onomu koji ga predaje.

1446
00:39:52,699 --> 00:39:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tomu bi čovjeku bolje bilo da se ni rodio nije.

1447
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] I dok su blagovali, on uze kruh iz reče blagoslov pa razlobi.

1448
00:39:59,639 --> 00:40:01,260
[SPEAKER_00] Razlobi, dade im i reče.

1449
00:40:01,260 --> 00:40:03,280
[SPEAKER_00] Uzmite, ovo je tijelo moje.

1450
00:40:03,280 --> 00:40:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] I uze čašu, zahvali i dade im.

1451
00:40:05,420 --> 00:40:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] I svi su izljepili.

1452
00:40:06,599 --> 00:40:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] A od im reče.

1453
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je krv moja, krv saveza, koja se za mnoge proljeva.

1454
00:40:12,739 --> 00:40:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje ćemo objasniti.

1455
00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:17,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne za sve, nego za mnoge.

1456
00:40:18,539 --> 00:40:21,139
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerojatno, možda neki do sad niste nije razumijeli razliku.

1457
00:40:21,139 --> 00:40:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] Čuli je zapravo razliku.

1458
00:40:23,039 --> 00:40:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zaista kažem vam, ne, neću više piti od ovoga roda trsova

1459
00:40:27,119 --> 00:40:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] do onoga dana kad ću ga novoga piti u kraljevstvu Božem.

1460
00:40:31,860 --> 00:40:37,059
[SPEAKER_00] Gotovo kao što je opisano u egzodusu Rabah ili u prorok Izalje.

1461
00:40:37,059 --> 00:40:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, i dalje, Luka 22, 28-30 isto.

1462
00:40:41,619 --> 00:40:43,860
[SPEAKER_00] Da, vi ste sa mnom ustrali u mojim kušnjama.

1463
00:40:43,860 --> 00:40:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vam s toga u bašenu predajam kraljevstvu što ga je meni predao moj otac.

1464
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] Da jedete i pijete za mojim stolom u kraljevstvu Mojemu

1465
00:40:52,099 --> 00:40:56,300
[SPEAKER_00] i sjedite na prijestoljima sudeći 12 plemena Izrelovih.

1466
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:57,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, evo.

1467
00:40:57,699 --> 00:41:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vi ste ti po kojima se po ovoj gozbi ovdje sada,

1468
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] tu ste 12 torica i vi ćete suditi 12 plemena Izrelovih.

1469
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste novi vođe 12 plemena Izrelovih.

1470
00:41:08,260 --> 00:41:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] Tako ih skuplja.

1471
00:41:09,059 --> 00:41:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, e sada, prije nego što krenemo,

1472
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju govorite o Isusovom času,

1473
00:41:15,559 --> 00:41:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] kada će sve ljude privući k sebi,

1474
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:19,820
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ne samo raspršene Izraelce,

1475
00:41:19,820 --> 00:41:23,300
[SPEAKER_00] nego sve ljude, isto preko križe Euharistije,

1476
00:41:23,300 --> 00:41:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] idemo samo ovdje riješiti problematiku

1477
00:41:27,739 --> 00:41:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] da se njegova krv proljeva za mnoge,

1478
00:41:30,699 --> 00:41:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] a ne za sve.

1479
00:41:31,619 --> 00:41:35,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znate da na svetoj misi, u Hrvatskom,

1480
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:37,559
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo uvijek tolerantni,

1481
00:41:37,559 --> 00:41:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] pa kažemo,

1482
00:41:38,440 --> 00:41:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je, kak ide?

1483
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj, ja čitam.

1484
00:41:44,539 --> 00:41:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] Vi slušate, ste zapamtili kak to ide.

1485
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:48,699
[SPEAKER_00] Više sam 8 godina svećenik,

1486
00:41:48,699 --> 00:41:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] ili...

1487
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

1488
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] Koja se proljeva za vas i za sve ljude.

1489
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je važno.

1490
00:41:53,579 --> 00:41:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] I odvaja za vas i za sve ljude.

1491
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ne kaže, koja se za sve vas proljeva,

1492
00:41:59,219 --> 00:42:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] nego za vas i za sve ljude.

1493
00:42:01,239 --> 00:42:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zapamtite ovu distinkciju koja se ovdje radi.

1494
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i ovdje.

1495
00:42:08,039 --> 00:42:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] Isto kaže, dakle, ovo je krv, moja krv saveza,

1496
00:42:11,699 --> 00:42:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] koja se za mnoge proljeva.

1497
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] E sada, stvar je u tome,

1498
00:42:18,420 --> 00:42:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] da kada radimo ovdje u svetoj misi,

1499
00:42:20,900 --> 00:42:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] recimo i u latinskom isto,

1500
00:42:24,059 --> 00:42:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] pro multis, ne pro omnibus,

1501
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] nego pro multis, za mnoge.

1502
00:42:27,940 --> 00:42:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, stvar je u tome,

1503
00:42:30,099 --> 00:42:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] kada se ovdje radi razlika za vas,

1504
00:42:32,460 --> 00:42:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] za židove i za sve ostale.

1505
00:42:35,840 --> 00:42:37,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i za pogane.

1506
00:42:38,039 --> 00:42:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] U hrvatskom, iako sam malo tražio,

1507
00:42:40,039 --> 00:42:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] nema hrvatski samo to,

1508
00:42:41,460 --> 00:42:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] ovo imaju drugi neki živi jezici

1509
00:42:43,519 --> 00:42:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] koji isto tako naprave.

1510
00:42:44,699 --> 00:42:46,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kada se ovdje kaže za mnoge,

1511
00:42:46,639 --> 00:42:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] multitudo, dakle, ovdje je riječ

1512
00:42:50,940 --> 00:42:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] o velikom mnoštvu.

1513
00:42:53,239 --> 00:42:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] I to multitudo ima univerzalno značenje.

1514
00:42:56,460 --> 00:42:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znači samo mnogo,

1515
00:42:58,159 --> 00:42:59,739
[SPEAKER_00] nego može značiti i sve.

1516
00:42:59,739 --> 00:43:01,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kada se kaže ovdje za mnoge,

1517
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje je spojeno sve,

1518
00:43:03,579 --> 00:43:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje je spojeno vi i oni.

1519
00:43:06,619 --> 00:43:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kada se kaže, govorim sada o jezišoj distinkciji,

1520
00:43:09,500 --> 00:43:10,780
[SPEAKER_00] govorim sada o jeziku.

1521
00:43:10,780 --> 00:43:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje je jezik problem,

1522
00:43:11,900 --> 00:43:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je problem spasenja.

1523
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da je Isus umro za svakoga.

1524
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] Za svakoga i za svakoga je prolio svoju krv.

1525
00:43:18,619 --> 00:43:19,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da se razumijemo.

1526
00:43:19,920 --> 00:43:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovdje je problem,

1527
00:43:21,579 --> 00:43:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] zašto vam ovo govorim,

1528
00:43:22,639 --> 00:43:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] ako vas neko pita,

1529
00:43:23,559 --> 00:43:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] kao što sam ja imao,

1530
00:43:24,500 --> 00:43:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam recimo imao problem s tim.

1531
00:43:26,460 --> 00:43:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam počeo kužiti tu razliku,

1532
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam počeo učiti jezike,

1533
00:43:30,219 --> 00:43:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] anavajte, učiti jezike ponekad može biti komno za vašu vjeru.

1534
00:43:33,500 --> 00:43:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kada sam kužio u latinskom promultis,

1535
00:43:37,079 --> 00:43:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] vidim u grčkom isto tako,

1536
00:43:38,539 --> 00:43:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] u izvodniku isto tako za mnoge,

1537
00:43:40,139 --> 00:43:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] a ovdje za vas i za sve.

1538
00:43:41,840 --> 00:43:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, riječ je da za mnoge,

1539
00:43:44,340 --> 00:43:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] podrazumljiva za vas,

1540
00:43:45,539 --> 00:43:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] židove,

1541
00:43:46,119 --> 00:43:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] on pred sovima židove,

1542
00:43:47,199 --> 00:43:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] ima dvanestoricu.

1543
00:43:48,199 --> 00:43:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i za sve.

1544
00:43:50,340 --> 00:43:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo sve, misli se, za ostale,

1545
00:43:52,539 --> 00:43:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] za pogane,

1546
00:43:54,619 --> 00:43:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] za oni koji nisu židovi,

1547
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] za ne židove,

1548
00:43:56,599 --> 00:43:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] za grke, rimljane itd.

1549
00:43:58,099 --> 00:44:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zaključit ćemo sa onaj Isusov čas,

1550
00:44:01,460 --> 00:44:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] kada će sve ljude privući k sebi.

1551
00:44:03,739 --> 00:44:06,219
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ono, konačno sabiranje svih plemena.

1552
00:44:06,219 --> 00:44:11,400
[SPEAKER_00] Iva dvanest, dvadeset do tristri kaže ovo.

1553
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:16,639
[SPEAKER_00] A među onima koji su došli klanjati na blagdan,

1554
00:44:16,639 --> 00:44:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] bijahu i neki grci.

1555
00:44:18,840 --> 00:44:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] Oni pristupe Filipu,

1556
00:44:20,119 --> 00:44:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] grčko ime,

1557
00:44:21,159 --> 00:44:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] naravno da će Filipu,

1558
00:44:22,460 --> 00:44:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] zoveš se Filip pa se daš,

1559
00:44:24,739 --> 00:44:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] jel da?

1560
00:44:25,019 --> 00:44:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] Filipu iz Becajde, Galilejske,

1561
00:44:27,239 --> 00:44:27,860
[SPEAKER_00] pa ga zamole.

1562
00:44:27,860 --> 00:44:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine, htjeli bismo vidjeti Isusa.

1563
00:44:29,800 --> 00:44:32,300
[SPEAKER_00] Filip ode i kaže to Adri,

1564
00:44:32,300 --> 00:44:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] drugo grčko ime,

1565
00:44:33,360 --> 00:44:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] ili tako?

1566
00:44:33,820 --> 00:44:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] Pogansko ime.

1567
00:44:35,159 --> 00:44:36,320
[SPEAKER_00] Pa Adri i Filip,

1568
00:44:36,320 --> 00:44:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] dva židova grčkih imena,

1569
00:44:38,079 --> 00:44:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] odu i kažu Isusu.

1570
00:44:39,920 --> 00:44:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] Isus im odgovori,

1571
00:44:41,059 --> 00:44:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] došao je čas da se proslavi sin čovječi.

1572
00:44:43,619 --> 00:44:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je sad ovo taj čas?

1573
00:44:45,519 --> 00:44:47,280
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto cijelo vrijeme odgađa čas i kaže,

1574
00:44:48,840 --> 00:44:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] u istom evanđelju po Ivanu,

1575
00:44:51,199 --> 00:44:52,219
[SPEAKER_00] druga glava,

1576
00:44:52,219 --> 00:44:53,679
[SPEAKER_00] kada Marija kaže,

1577
00:44:53,679 --> 00:44:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] vi da nemaju,

1578
00:44:54,699 --> 00:44:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] a on kaže,

1579
00:44:55,699 --> 00:44:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] ženo, što je vam s tobom,

1580
00:44:56,900 --> 00:44:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] još nije došao moj čas.

1581
00:44:58,119 --> 00:44:59,780
[SPEAKER_00] Još neki, još nije došao moj čas.

1582
00:44:59,780 --> 00:45:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nego sada,

1583
00:45:00,500 --> 00:45:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ovo je trenutak?

1584
00:45:01,920 --> 00:45:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Došao je čas.

1585
00:45:03,199 --> 00:45:04,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ga traže grci,

1586
00:45:04,300 --> 00:45:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] jer ga traže pogani.

1587
00:45:05,340 --> 00:45:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] Došao je čas, jel?

1588
00:45:07,599 --> 00:45:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, čim su pogani počeli tražiti Isusa,

1589
00:45:10,920 --> 00:45:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže,

1590
00:45:12,159 --> 00:45:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] sada je došao,

1591
00:45:13,159 --> 00:45:14,139
[SPEAKER_00] došao moj čas.

1592
00:45:14,139 --> 00:45:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] To je to, ispunjenje, jel?

1593
00:45:15,300 --> 00:45:16,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne samo židovima,

1594
00:45:16,719 --> 00:45:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] nego i poganima.

1595
00:45:17,780 --> 00:45:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da se proslavi sin čovječi.

1596
00:45:19,619 --> 00:45:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda govor,

1597
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:22,559
[SPEAKER_00] zaista, zaista kaže vam,

1598
00:45:22,559 --> 00:45:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] ako pšenično zrno,

1599
00:45:23,559 --> 00:45:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] pavši na zemlju,

1600
00:45:24,460 --> 00:45:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] ne umre,

1601
00:45:24,840 --> 00:45:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] ostaje samo,

1602
00:45:25,579 --> 00:45:26,440
[SPEAKER_00] a ko ne umre,

1603
00:45:26,440 --> 00:45:27,820
[SPEAKER_00] donosi objelat rod.

1604
00:45:27,820 --> 00:45:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vidite,

1605
00:45:28,639 --> 00:45:30,780
[SPEAKER_00] poveznica između smrti i hrane,

1606
00:45:30,780 --> 00:45:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] pšenično zrno, jel?

1607
00:45:31,960 --> 00:45:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] Između, dakle,

1608
00:45:33,119 --> 00:45:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] prehramdenog neke namjednice

1609
00:45:35,199 --> 00:45:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] i smrti.

1610
00:45:36,199 --> 00:45:38,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, opet imamo gozba,

1611
00:45:38,639 --> 00:45:40,480
[SPEAKER_00] koja će zapravo biti smrtolosna,

1612
00:45:40,480 --> 00:45:43,260
[SPEAKER_00] kako će izgledati taj čas.

1613
00:45:43,260 --> 00:45:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] I ono,

1614
00:45:44,119 --> 00:45:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] tko ljubi svoj život,

1615
00:45:44,940 --> 00:45:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] izgubi će ga,

1616
00:45:45,539 --> 00:45:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] tko brzi svoj život na ovom svijetu,

1617
00:45:47,019 --> 00:45:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] sačuvat će ga za život vječni.

1618
00:45:49,079 --> 00:45:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] E, sada,

1619
00:45:49,880 --> 00:45:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] u to dođe glas s neba.

1620
00:45:53,599 --> 00:45:54,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je taj glas s neba?

1621
00:45:54,840 --> 00:45:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] Očev glas.

1622
00:45:55,659 --> 00:45:56,719
[SPEAKER_00] Samo tri puta,

1623
00:45:56,719 --> 00:45:58,579
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je treći i posljednji puta,

1624
00:45:58,579 --> 00:45:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] kada u Evanđelju

1625
00:45:59,440 --> 00:46:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] imamo očev glas,

1626
00:46:00,500 --> 00:46:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] glas s neba.

1627
00:46:01,199 --> 00:46:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je treći i posljednji puta,

1628
00:46:03,139 --> 00:46:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] kada čujemo da otac nebeski govori.

1629
00:46:05,940 --> 00:46:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] U to dođe glas s neba.

1630
00:46:07,880 --> 00:46:10,300
[SPEAKER_00] Proslavio sam i opet ću proslaviti.

1631
00:46:10,300 --> 00:46:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mnoštvo koje je od nje stajalo

1632
00:46:12,019 --> 00:46:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] i slušalo,

1633
00:46:12,599 --> 00:46:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] govoraše za grbjelo je.

1634
00:46:13,900 --> 00:46:15,219
[SPEAKER_00] Drugi govorahu,

1635
00:46:15,219 --> 00:46:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] anđel mu je zborio.

1636
00:46:16,380 --> 00:46:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] Isus na to reče,

1637
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj glas nije bio poradi mene,

1638
00:46:19,519 --> 00:46:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] nego poradi vas.

1639
00:46:20,599 --> 00:46:23,320
[SPEAKER_00] Sada je sud ovome svijetu,

1640
00:46:23,320 --> 00:46:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] sada će knez ovoga svijeta biti izbačen.

1641
00:46:27,099 --> 00:46:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, križ kao univerzalni egzorcizam.

1642
00:46:29,659 --> 00:46:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, možemo imati ciklus kateheza

1643
00:46:33,659 --> 00:46:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] na temu križ kao univerzalni egzorcizam.

1644
00:46:37,880 --> 00:46:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što isto imamo, dakle,

1645
00:46:43,019 --> 00:46:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] kod proroka Ezekijela,

1646
00:46:45,239 --> 00:46:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] kod proroka Ezekijela se stavlja znak križa na čelu,

1647
00:46:49,420 --> 00:46:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] da se zna, dakle, isto neki ukrštani znak.

1648
00:46:52,039 --> 00:46:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, imate te povezanost križa i egzorcizma

1649
00:46:54,980 --> 00:46:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] isto kod proroka, isto u starom zajetu i tako dalje.

1650
00:46:57,699 --> 00:46:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] To isto može biti jedno zadimljivo.

1651
00:46:59,440 --> 00:47:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ok, možda, jednog dana.

1652
00:47:01,579 --> 00:47:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sada će knez ovoga svijeta biti izbačen.

1653
00:47:04,599 --> 00:47:06,219
[SPEAKER_00] Križ kao univerzalni egzorcizam.

1654
00:47:06,219 --> 00:47:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] A ja kada budem uznignut sa zemlje,

1655
00:47:09,199 --> 00:47:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] sve ću privući k sebi.

1656
00:47:10,800 --> 00:47:13,139
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ću privući k sebi.

1657
00:47:13,139 --> 00:47:13,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sve.

1658
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mnoge, nego sve ću privući k sebi.

1659
00:47:16,500 --> 00:47:20,679
[SPEAKER_00] I sada, ovdje mi je onako se lijepo zaključuje, zaokružuje.

1660
00:47:20,679 --> 00:47:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, imate ovaj, kak se zove,

1661
00:47:24,619 --> 00:47:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] pardon, pardon, pardon, pardon.

1662
00:47:27,300 --> 00:47:30,179
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, kada će to biti,

1663
00:47:30,179 --> 00:47:34,219
[SPEAKER_00] kada budem uznignut sa zemlje,

1664
00:47:34,219 --> 00:47:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] sve ću privući k sebi.

1665
00:47:35,119 --> 00:47:37,219
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, on će privući svek sebi kada bude što?

1666
00:47:37,219 --> 00:47:38,159
[SPEAKER_00] Uzdignut.

1667
00:47:38,159 --> 00:47:40,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kada je sve Isus uznignut?

1668
00:47:40,340 --> 00:47:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kada je sve Isus uznignut?

1669
00:47:42,019 --> 00:47:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] Križ, uznignut je u trenutku skrsnuća,

1670
00:47:46,500 --> 00:47:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] uznignut je u trenutku uzašašća.

1671
00:47:49,380 --> 00:47:51,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kada, jer uznašašćem,

1672
00:47:51,139 --> 00:47:53,400
[SPEAKER_00] on kreće pripremati nebesku gozbu

1673
00:47:53,400 --> 00:47:55,639
[SPEAKER_00] i kada će on uznašašćem u nebu biti

1674
00:47:55,639 --> 00:47:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] naša stalna žrtva.

1675
00:47:57,039 --> 00:47:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] Stalno prinošenje samoga sveme gospodinu.

1676
00:47:59,360 --> 00:48:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je uznašašće važno.

1677
00:48:00,840 --> 00:48:04,780
[SPEAKER_00] I kada je još Isus uznignut sa zemlje?

1678
00:48:04,780 --> 00:48:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Na svakoj svetoj misi.

1679
00:48:07,420 --> 00:48:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je taj znak, to je ta gesta.

1680
00:48:09,599 --> 00:48:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] U najključnjem dijelu sve te mise,

1681
00:48:11,360 --> 00:48:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] pod pretvorom,

1682
00:48:12,420 --> 00:48:14,219
[SPEAKER_00] Krist je uznignut.

1683
00:48:14,679 --> 00:48:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sa zemlje.

1684
00:48:16,480 --> 00:48:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] I tada će sve privući k sebi.

1685
00:48:18,440 --> 00:48:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kolike sve te mise od posljednje večere

1686
00:48:20,940 --> 00:48:23,260
[SPEAKER_00] koje su privukle i obratile

1687
00:48:23,260 --> 00:48:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] na milijarde.

1688
00:48:24,500 --> 00:48:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ako uzmete stoljeća,

1689
00:48:27,500 --> 00:48:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] tisuć ljeća

1690
00:48:28,639 --> 00:48:30,139
[SPEAKER_00] koja su od posljednje večere

1691
00:48:30,139 --> 00:48:31,659
[SPEAKER_00] i od ovoga što se dogodilo

1692
00:48:31,659 --> 00:48:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] u vazbenom trodnevnju.

1693
00:48:34,340 --> 00:48:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] I zato, dakle, ovo,

1694
00:48:36,239 --> 00:48:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] a ja kad budem uznignut sa zemlje,

1695
00:48:38,179 --> 00:48:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] sve ću privući k sebi.

1696
00:48:39,960 --> 00:48:42,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Evanđelje nije poezija.

1697
00:48:43,900 --> 00:48:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] Isus ne koristi neke motive

1698
00:48:45,679 --> 00:48:47,099
[SPEAKER_00] poetično.

1699
00:48:47,099 --> 00:48:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] Uznignut sa zemlje,

1700
00:48:48,579 --> 00:48:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] sve ću preneseno.

1701
00:48:50,119 --> 00:48:52,179
[SPEAKER_00] Jer on govori,

1702
00:48:52,179 --> 00:48:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] što ono kad kaže,

1703
00:48:54,000 --> 00:48:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne jedete tijela sina čovječega,

1704
00:48:56,360 --> 00:48:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] ne pijete njegove krvi,

1705
00:48:57,480 --> 00:48:59,320
[SPEAKER_00] nemate života u sebi.

1706
00:48:59,320 --> 00:49:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad svi odlaze,

1707
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] što kaže?

1708
00:49:01,340 --> 00:49:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] Bada je šalio sam se,

1709
00:49:02,079 --> 00:49:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] to je metaforika,

1710
00:49:02,800 --> 00:49:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] to je simbolično značenje.

1711
00:49:04,019 --> 00:49:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, to je konkretno značenje,

1712
00:49:05,619 --> 00:49:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] to fakat tako stoji.

1713
00:49:07,039 --> 00:49:09,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovdje će stvarno biti uznignut sa zemlje

1714
00:49:09,639 --> 00:49:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] i stvarno će tada sve privući k sebi.

1715
00:49:11,860 --> 00:49:15,219
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono što sam na početku stavio

1716
00:49:15,219 --> 00:49:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] kod Izaije 11.10.20,

1717
00:49:17,059 --> 00:49:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] time smo i započeli.

1718
00:49:19,320 --> 00:49:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] U ovaj dan njišev izdanak Mesija

1719
00:49:21,440 --> 00:49:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] dignut kao stijeg narodima.

1720
00:49:23,920 --> 00:49:25,679
[SPEAKER_00] Uzdignut sa zemlje.

1721
00:49:25,679 --> 00:49:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, podignut će stijeg narodima

1722
00:49:28,400 --> 00:49:31,179
[SPEAKER_00] i on će biti dignut kao stijeg narodima.

1723
00:49:31,179 --> 00:49:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] Puci će ga željno tražiti.

1724
00:49:34,940 --> 00:49:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, svi bi ovdje zaključio.

1725
00:49:36,900 --> 00:49:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, je li ovo sve jasno?

1726
00:49:39,079 --> 00:49:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, razumijeli ste, dobro.

1727
00:49:41,880 --> 00:49:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] Još ne razumijete.

1728
00:49:43,119 --> 00:49:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, dobro.

1729
00:49:45,079 --> 00:49:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] Sljedeći puta, e sada,

1730
00:49:46,800 --> 00:49:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ono što sam rekao,

1731
00:49:48,420 --> 00:49:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] ovo sve, ako je sjelo,

1732
00:49:50,280 --> 00:49:52,139
[SPEAKER_00] onda smo prešli onu granicu,

1733
00:49:52,139 --> 00:49:56,239
[SPEAKER_00] dobro, Euharistija kao dio ispunjenja,

1734
00:49:56,239 --> 00:49:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] ne dio, ispunjenje, konkretno ispunjenje,

1735
00:49:58,860 --> 00:50:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je sve svih židovskih nada,

1736
00:50:01,300 --> 00:50:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] nada na iščekivanje i tako dalje.

1737
00:50:02,920 --> 00:50:04,860
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kroz proroke,

1738
00:50:04,860 --> 00:50:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] kroz, dakle, samu židovsku tradiciju

1739
00:50:07,980 --> 00:50:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] i naravno ono što je za našu odjelenu braću

1740
00:50:11,380 --> 00:50:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] isto važno, kroz same Isusove riječi.

1741
00:50:13,599 --> 00:50:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, gdje je tu onda ona konkretna prisutnost?

1742
00:50:17,519 --> 00:50:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš to, kažem,

1743
00:50:19,099 --> 00:50:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] kod Euharistije idemo još korak dalje

1744
00:50:21,119 --> 00:50:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] i kažemo da ta mesijanska gozba

1745
00:50:23,440 --> 00:50:25,500
[SPEAKER_00] nije samo gozba, dakle,

1746
00:50:25,500 --> 00:50:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] od žrtvovanoga, od pretiline i vina,

1747
00:50:27,500 --> 00:50:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] fina, staložene i tako dalje,

1748
00:50:29,139 --> 00:50:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] nego da pod tim žrtvovanom je njegovo tijelo,

1749
00:50:32,159 --> 00:50:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, pretilo,

1750
00:50:34,820 --> 00:50:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] nije su, tijelo bilo pretilo,

1751
00:50:36,559 --> 00:50:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] pa je zato pretilina,

1752
00:50:37,519 --> 00:50:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, dakle, meso,

1753
00:50:39,199 --> 00:50:41,360
[SPEAKER_00] nego i pod prilikama vina,

1754
00:50:41,360 --> 00:50:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] njegova krv.

1755
00:50:42,119 --> 00:50:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] zašto idemo u konkretnu prisutnost,

1756
00:50:44,340 --> 00:50:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] a ne samo neka gozba,

1757
00:50:45,460 --> 00:50:46,719
[SPEAKER_00] spome gozba i tako dalje.

1758
00:50:46,719 --> 00:50:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, sljedeći puta,

1759
00:50:48,139 --> 00:50:49,860
[SPEAKER_00] nazvao sam,

1760
00:50:49,860 --> 00:50:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] predavanje za sljedeći puta,

1761
00:50:52,340 --> 00:50:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] četvrta čaša

1762
00:50:53,619 --> 00:50:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] i nova paska,

1763
00:50:55,139 --> 00:50:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno izlazak.

1764
00:50:55,760 --> 00:50:57,800
[SPEAKER_00] Što je ta četvrta čaša?

1765
00:50:57,800 --> 00:50:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] Vi se sjećate da Isus kaže

1766
00:50:59,219 --> 00:51:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] u Gecemaniji,

1767
00:51:00,760 --> 00:51:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] oče, rekao sam,

1768
00:51:03,739 --> 00:51:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] ono što Isus govori nije poetično,

1769
00:51:05,840 --> 00:51:07,780
[SPEAKER_00] nego ima konkretno značenje.

1770
00:51:07,780 --> 00:51:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] Kada Isus kaže,

1771
00:51:08,719 --> 00:51:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] oče, ako je moguće,

1772
00:51:09,920 --> 00:51:11,880
[SPEAKER_00] neka me mi bojđe ova čaša

1773
00:51:11,880 --> 00:51:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] ili ovaj kalež,

1774
00:51:12,519 --> 00:51:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovisi, dakle, o prijevodu.

1775
00:51:13,960 --> 00:51:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] Od toga kaže preneseno,

1776
00:51:15,599 --> 00:51:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego koja je to čaša,

1777
00:51:16,920 --> 00:51:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] koja je to kalež.

1778
00:51:17,760 --> 00:51:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto, dakle,

1779
00:51:19,639 --> 00:51:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] kada ste imali slavlje pashe,

1780
00:51:21,679 --> 00:51:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, govorimo o živijevskom slavlju pashe,

1781
00:51:24,559 --> 00:51:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] prisutne su četiri čaše,

1782
00:51:27,199 --> 00:51:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] pashalne, četiri,

1783
00:51:28,480 --> 00:51:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] četiri kaleža pashalna.

1784
00:51:29,880 --> 00:51:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ključ,

1785
00:51:32,320 --> 00:51:33,320
[SPEAKER_00] da vidimo sad,

1786
00:51:33,320 --> 00:51:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] idemo korak dalje,

1787
00:51:34,239 --> 00:51:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] vidjeti kako iz živijevske perspektive

1788
00:51:36,860 --> 00:51:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] isto shvatiti,

1789
00:51:37,840 --> 00:51:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] da možda zaista riječi

1790
00:51:39,039 --> 00:51:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] o nekoj konkretnoj prisutnosti božarskoj

1791
00:51:41,380 --> 00:51:42,559
[SPEAKER_00] pod prilikama kruha i vijena.

1792
00:51:42,559 --> 00:51:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da sljedeći puta,

1793
00:51:43,880 --> 00:51:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] kako je zlala pashu Isus ovo vrijeme,

1794
00:51:45,679 --> 00:51:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] to nam je važno,

1795
00:51:46,500 --> 00:51:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] što su Petar i Ivan

1796
00:51:48,559 --> 00:51:49,800
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo činili

1797
00:51:49,800 --> 00:51:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] kada su otešli u Jeruzalem

1798
00:51:51,340 --> 00:51:52,280
[SPEAKER_00] pripraviti pashu,

1799
00:51:52,280 --> 00:51:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, to je detalj

1800
00:51:53,900 --> 00:51:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji tako pročitamo

1801
00:51:54,940 --> 00:51:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] i prođemo.

1802
00:51:55,440 --> 00:51:56,679
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, vrlo značajno,

1803
00:51:56,679 --> 00:51:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo važno.

1804
00:51:57,380 --> 00:51:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto su četiri čaše vina

1805
00:51:59,639 --> 00:52:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] potrebne za svako slavlje pashe?

1806
00:52:01,500 --> 00:52:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji su dijelovi razine,

1807
00:52:04,000 --> 00:52:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći,

1808
00:52:04,559 --> 00:52:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji je red slavljena pashe?

1809
00:52:06,000 --> 00:52:07,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ordo pashe,

1810
00:52:07,280 --> 00:52:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći,

1811
00:52:08,019 --> 00:52:09,699
[SPEAKER_00] i kako odgovaraju dijelovima

1812
00:52:09,699 --> 00:52:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] redu svete mise?

1813
00:52:10,880 --> 00:52:13,260
[SPEAKER_00] I je li Isus zapravo

1814
00:52:13,260 --> 00:52:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] zaključio posljednju večeru?

1815
00:52:15,579 --> 00:52:20,320
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što nas čeka sljedeći puta.

1816
00:52:20,320 --> 00:52:20,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ok?

1817
00:52:20,679 --> 00:52:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] Sljedeći utorak,

1818
00:52:21,820 --> 00:52:22,820
[SPEAKER_00] vidimo se ovdje.

1819
00:52:22,820 --> 00:52:23,639
[SPEAKER_00] Evo.

1820
00:52:32,119 --> 00:52:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1821
00:52:32,559 --> 00:52:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo sada nešto jesti pit.

1822
00:52:34,179 --> 00:52:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] Toko o gozbi i tako dalje,

1823
00:52:36,380 --> 00:52:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno ste ogladnili.

1824
00:52:37,280 --> 00:52:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1825
00:52:38,059 --> 00:52:40,320
[SPEAKER_00] U ima Oca i Sina i Duha Svetoga.

1826
00:52:40,320 --> 00:52:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

1827
00:52:40,699 --> 00:52:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] Slava Ocu i Sinu i Duhu Svetomu,

1828
00:52:43,460 --> 00:52:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi jaš na početku,

1829
00:52:45,480 --> 00:52:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] tako i sada i vazda,

1830
00:52:47,380 --> 00:52:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] i u vijeke, vijekova.

1831
00:52:49,199 --> 00:52:49,719
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

1832
00:52:49,719 --> 00:52:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] U ima Oca i Sina i Duha Svetoga.

1833
00:52:51,619 --> 00:52:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

